window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>So, Jacob’s the son of Lucifer.&nbsp;</p> <p>Unfortunately, he can’t think about that right now, because several Demon Kings are still trying to kill his ass and take over the Fourth Circle.&nbsp;</p> <p>Jake’s not about to let that happen.&nbsp;</p> <p>He needs to get more powerful, and fast. To do that, he needs more Demon Lords.&nbsp;</p> <p>Now, where can he get more of those?&nbsp;</p> <p>\\Well, he does have seven loyal succubi and one stoned imp at his side....</p>"; 
